<HR> <P>
<H2><A NAME=SECTION00135100000000000000> Translate Operation</A></H2>
<P>
	<A NAME=est-tr HREF="est-trbig.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="" SRC="est-tr.gif"></A>
	<A HREF="est-trbig.gif">Figure (est-tr): Translating a Torus</A>
<P>
<tt>mged&gt; <em>Select the ``Translate'' entry in the solid edit menu</em> <BR>mged&gt; <em>p -.5 -1 .5</em> <BR>mged&gt;
</tt>
<P>
The vertex V of the torus is moved to (-.5, -1, .5).
See 
	<A HREF="est-trbig.gif">Figure (est-tr)</A>
.  The
coordinates of the other points remain the same, relative to the vertex.
The command
<P>
<tt>mged&gt; <em>p 0 0 0</em> <BR>mged&gt;
</tt>
<P>
will restore the original position.
<P>
